data.description: Mountain views from the deck of this 2,056 square foot home. Property is just over 51 acres in 3 parcels. 30x40 shop and several outbuildings. Fenced yard. Ready for horses and other livestock. Cross fencing is in place. Chicken coop, goat barn, large shop. Two large walnut trees.  Main level has a large living room and dining area with a nice kitchen with island. The basement with it's own entrance has a 252 square foot dog/animal grooming salon. Motion Detector Security lights.  County maintained road. Close to Tonasket
